{
  "id": "6a15857edf1e77ecb667b939",
  "title": "人狼ゲームの構造的衰退",
  "created": 1779795337,
  "updated": 1779795350,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a15857edf1e77ecb667b939",
      "text": "人狼ゲームの構造的衰退",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795337,
      "updated": 1779795337
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15857e000000000017de58",
      "text": "[tokoroten.icon]のClaudeのログから自動抽出された記事",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795337,
      "updated": 1779795337
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15857f000000000017de59",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795337,
      "updated": 1779795337
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158580000000000017de5a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795338,
      "updated": 1779795338
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de5c",
      "text": "人狼ゲームが流行→衰退した因果。表面的な「民度問題」の下にゲーム設計上の必然がある。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de5e",
      "text": "[*** 流行 (2012-2013)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de5f",
      "text": "\t2012年初頭: ニコ動でゲーム実況者のボイチャ人狼が増殖",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de60",
      "text": "\t同年5月: ニコ生公式番組",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de61",
      "text": "\t2013年: テレビで取り上げ → 知名度爆発",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de62",
      "text": "\tタレント/俳優の騙し合いが映像コンテンツとして強かった",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de63",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de64",
      "text": "[*** 衰退の4要因 (上から構造的)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de66",
      "text": "[** 1. テンプレ化・定石ガチガチ問題]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de67",
      "text": "「自由議論」のはずが「霊能ローラー」等の定石押付に変質。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de68",
      "text": "「村利」の名のもと、声の大きい上級者が自由なプレイを排除。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de6a",
      "text": "[** 2. 初心者の参入障壁]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de6b",
      "text": "ルール+役職+専門用語 (占いCO/護衛/対抗/ローラー) を知らないと戦力にならず、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de6c",
      "text": "[* 「初心者CO NG」] つまり初心者を自称すること自体が許されない空気。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de6e",
      "text": "[** 3. ゲーム構造上の弱点]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de6f",
      "text": "\t必要人数多い、集めにくい",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de70",
      "text": "\t1試合が長く終わりが読めない",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de71",
      "text": "\t初日吊られた/噛まれた人がやることない (脱落者の暇問題)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de72",
      "text": "\t嘘や詰めが苦手な人を弾く",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de73",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de74",
      "text": "[** 4. 代替コンテンツ]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de75",
      "text": "\tAmong Us (2020〜) が人狼的心理戦の需要を吸収",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de76",
      "text": "\tソシャゲ/Steam/Switch で短時間ゲームが充実 → 大人数長時間拘束の優先度低下",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de78",
      "text": "[*** 共通する核]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de79",
      "text": "ところてん自身の整理 (turn 2):",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de7b",
      "text": "> 議論フェイズは難癖をつけて疑うか、COでコントロールするか、そしてそれを前提とした戦略理解がないと成立せず、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de7c",
      "text": "> 初日につられた・食われた人はやることが無いので、パーティーゲームとして微妙",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de7d",
      "text": "> そもそも、CO以外で思ったように情報が増えないことも問題",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de7e",
      "text": "> 結果として、繰り返し遊ぶことを前提の行動になってしまい、それについていけない初心者が脱落",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de7f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de80",
      "text": "つまり「繰り返し前提のメタゲーム化」が新規排除の構造になっている。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de82",
      "text": "→ メタ化したフレームワーク: [客観情報が乏しい集団の必然帰結]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a15858c000000000017de83",
      "text": "→ 後発はどう対処したか: [後発人狼系の構造的回避策]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795350,
      "updated": 1779795350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158580000000000017de5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795338,
      "updated": 1779795338
    }
  ]
}